<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: #10B981; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
    .content { background: #f9fafb; padding: 30px; }
    .amount { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #10B981; }
    .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background: #4F46E5; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Payout Approved!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi there,</p>
      <p>Great news! Your payout request has been approved.</p>
      <p><strong>Approved Amount:</strong> <span class="amount">${{formatCurrency payoutRequest.amountCents}}</span></p>
      <p><strong>Request ID:</strong> {{payoutRequest.id}}</p>
      <p>Your payout will be processed shortly and sent to your registered payout method.</p>
      <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="button">View Details</a>
      <p>Best regards,<br>The Voyage Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>


